{"tid":407843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺香港地做牛真係好撚慘","createTime":"2017-09-20T17:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T03:17:28.000Z","uid":81684,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"51d3da91e69a89d027e083bd062d7e5d222fb834","tid":407843,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=766282640210433&amp;id=304430556395646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D766282640210433%26id%3D304430556395646&d=dmzxkdd1Kkw2ixG9jwRT5JWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0063d8fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=766282640210433&amp;id=304430556395646</a><br />\n<br />\n班十四鄉村牛關注組真係痴撚線<br />\n以為入面有bb就喺條街直接劏開<br />\n人地護牛天使follow開班牛<br />\n人地話一定無又唔撚聽<br />\n劏完無bb又話人地馬後砲<br />\n又有件八婆師奶喺隔離嘈喧巴閉<br />\n然後成班柒頭跌咗落地拿返咗渣沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後呢<br />\n最後用個勾勾撚住隻牛女上車<br />\n雖然死咗啫<br />\n屌你都執返好啲內臟等人好好睇睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無人性 無專業知識<br />\n想做好事搏出位都唔係咁撚樣㗎<br />\n平時啲牛比車撞死都算<br />\n仲要比班戇鳩村民仲要捅多刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6e5d52bc1e92502db943f993a8dc9a49a3c995","tid":407843,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j0de72c5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj0de72c5&h=8afb0871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n護牛天使啲人同警察傾計都比啲仆街攞住部ipad偷聽又影住人 好撚無品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a63fc467d202146eb96bc655e0a1936008e6e96","tid":407843,"uid":125237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739183067837f9e1a6d1041236ac8c9ea9c72277","tid":407843,"uid":89957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:58:44.000Z","msg":"幫推 推上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60069d9c7e1327189fe74ff88d81bdc0f8a24b1","tid":407843,"uid":12444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:59:58.000Z","msg":"幫推....呢班廢老真係正仆街  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c690c4a123a5f269400b28447deeaa33708fcae7","tid":407843,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"人仲慘"},{"pid":"2dc544f6ddec9967a77c03b8860aec7c2f0fc650","tid":407843,"uid":12444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T03:03:06.000Z","msg":"根本就為上報為出名....真心鍾意牛 點會咁樣對條牛屍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3d569b2b90bb68496cfc5208fab0cfa64865d5","tid":407843,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"牛屎地方係咁上下架啦"},{"pid":"6939ab9e221be1a90a43e3c7297d4cc415e20362","tid":407843,"uid":48913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T03:15:25.000Z","msg":"屌搵個獸醫一摸就知啦 喺到鳩估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157eebe648390df83ae10f10afbd939b19030901","tid":407843,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T03:17:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}